title: Other Currency Held in the Treasury, Treasury and Federal Reserve Banks for United States
notes:
Series Is Presented Here As Three Variables--(1)--Original Data, 1878-1914 (2)--Original Data, 1914-1920 (3)--Original Data, 1919-1949. Data Exclude Figures For Gold, Silver, And National Bank Notes. First Of Month Data From The Source Are Shown Here As End Of The Month Figures. Source: U.S. Treasury Department.

This NBER data series m14134a appears on the NBER website in Chapter 14 at http://www.nber.org/databases/macrohistory/contents/chapter14.html.
